title: Who Am I ?: Discovering Your Identity
description: Millions have lived and died without ever maximizing potential and fulfilling purpose. This book, WHO AM I ?, will revolutionize your life. It will open your eyes to the importance of your identity, a vital revelation that is paramount to the fulfilment of purpose and destiny. Do not make a next step, make another important decision, until you have consumed the contents of this book, applied its principles, and have God's perspective about yourself. When you know who you are, you will experience fulfillment and gain meaning to life. I wish for you the best as you take this journey in the discovery of who your are.
author: Dameyan O. Cole
